movie.title: Apollo 11
movie.plot: A look at the Apollo 11 mission to land on the moon led by commander Neil Armstrong and pilots Buzz Aldrin and Michael Collins.
movie.awards: Nominated for 1 BAFTA Film Award. Another 52 wins & 35 nominations.
